{
  "chapter": 20,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十回\"蜂女飞兵\"：黄河香舟上，姚四妹挑战易清菊，以亮银飞钩划圈比武，被易清菊趁其招式空门击败，踝骨碎裂。蜂女们群起围攻，易清菊以一敌四，水灵光亦力战蜂女欲救被制穴道的铁中棠。易冰梅与花大姑飞上帆上横木比斗轻功，约定先抢上船桅者胜，二人各展奇谋，易冰梅断桅、花大姑踢帆借力，最终以内力相拼僵持不下。铁中棠为解水灵光之危，毅然跃入黄河急流，杨八妹不顾危险跳水相救。此时霹雳火乘舟赶来寻海大少，花大姑巧言周旋。海大少突然现身舱门，原来被人暗中救出，花大姑以旧情恳求海大少暂缓算账。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "姚四妹",
      "listener": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "text": "大姐，不如就让妹子我陪易姑娘走两招吧，妹子若侥幸胜了，就让这位公子陪着我好么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "speaker_name": "易清菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "text": "你若败了呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "姚四妹",
      "listener": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "text": "妹子我若是败了，就让别的姐妹再陪两位易姑娘走几招。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "speaker_name": "易清菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "text": "哎哟，好姑娘，你们真聪明呀，这样说来，便宜岂不是都让你姐妹们占了么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "姚四妹",
      "listener": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "text": "好姐姐，你看我年纪轻，就让我一招吧！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "speaker_name": "易清菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "text": "好是好，就只一样不好。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "姚四妹",
      "listener": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "text": "什么不好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "speaker_name": "易清菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "text": "你这样水造似的一个人儿，姐姐我若是失手伤了你，心里该多么难受呀！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "姚四妹",
      "listener": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "text": "不会的，我知道姐姐你心地最好，绝对狠不了心伤人的。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "李二姐",
      "listener": "char_nv_chuan_jia",
      "text": "咱们若没有姚四妹，当真还不知谁来对付这易清菊呢！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nv_chuan_jia",
      "speaker_name": "杨八妹",
      "listener": "char_xing_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "有了姚四妹，也未见能对付得了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "speaker_name": "易清菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "text": "是呀，真狠不了心伤你，咱们就好歹试试看吧，但……咱们在哪儿动手呢？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "姚四妹",
      "listener": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "text": "反正是咱们姐妹闹着玩的，哪里动手，不部一样么？就在船头吧！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "易冰梅",
      "listener": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "text": "这妮子鬼得很，你要小心了。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "speaker_name": "易清菊",
      "listener": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "text": "她还鬼得过我么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_ling_guang",
      "speaker_name": "水灵光",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你放心……",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "姚四妹",
      "listener": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "text": "咱们姐妹就在这圈子里走两招好么？谁若出了圈子，就算输了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "姚四妹",
      "listener": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "text": "易姐姐，你不用兵刃么？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "speaker_name": "易清菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "text": "好妹子，你只管用吧！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "姚四妹",
      "listener": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "text": "多谢姐姐。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "speaker_name": "易清菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "text": "哎哟，好厉害的小蜂子，说打就打呀！好，姐姐让你三招。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "speaker_name": "易清菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "text": "哎哟，三招让不成，就让你两招算了！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "姚四妹",
      "listener": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "text": "好姐姐，我上了你的当了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "speaker_name": "易清菊",
      "listener": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "text": "哎哟，好妹妹，是不是我下手太重，伤了你呀？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "speaker_name": "易清菊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这只手真该死，连轻重都不知道，幸好伤了脚，还没有伤了她如花似玉的脸蛋……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "text": "你虽未伤她的脸蛋，但一个大姑娘，脚若是跛子，怎么嫁得出去呀？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "speaker_name": "易清菊",
      "listener": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "text": "那倒没有关系，我九弟也是跛子，这位妹妹若是跛子，正好和我九弟凑成一对。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "易冰梅",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我那九弟虽跛了，但心计却是干灵百巧，若不是他，咱们还找不到这里。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "speaker_name": "易清菊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么你们这些如花似玉的美人儿，也会群殴？花大姑，这就是你教出来的么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "text": "谁教你伤了咱们四妹呀！她们就是要群殴，我这做姐姐的，也没有什么法子。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "姚四妹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好姐姐，你们都别想走了吧，好歹先赔我一只脚来。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "speaker_name": "易清菊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我赔你！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_ling_guang",
      "speaker_name": "水灵光",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你伤在什……什么穴道？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_shui_ling_guang",
      "text": "相门……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_shui_ling_guang",
      "text": "灵光，闪开！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "易冰梅",
      "listener": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "text": "让小妹妹们在船头动手，咱们两人到舱里去。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "text": "就在这里又有何妨？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "易冰梅",
      "listener": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "text": "我与你动手之间，可有别人出手相助？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "text": "还有谁来相助？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "text": "你我都是做大姐的，便该拿出做大姐的样子来，拳打脚踢地动手，岂非让人见了笑话？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "易冰梅",
      "listener": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "text": "如何动手，但凭吩咐。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "text": "来！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "易冰梅",
      "listener": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "text": "比什么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "text": "你我谁先抢上这船桅，便是谁胜了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "易冰梅",
      "listener": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "text": "若是谁也抢不上呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "text": "活着的就算胜了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "易冰梅",
      "listener": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "text": "何时开始？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "text": "你我两人走到中央，互相一掌，掌声响时，便是开始。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "易冰梅",
      "listener": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "text": "好！我这一掌若是将你震死，就不必比了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "text": "易姑娘，你真聪明！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "text": "好美的手！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "蜂女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姐妹们，莫要伤了她的性命，只将她脚踝捏碎就算了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "姚四妹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还要加些利息，要两只脚。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "speaker_name": "易清菊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好妹子，你们不怕我的兄弟姐妹问你要利息么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "蜂女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姐妹们，你们过来一个，帮帮忙好么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "李二姐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好了，他跳下去了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "蜂女们",
      "listener": "char_xing_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_ling_guang",
      "speaker_name": "水灵光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你们……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_ling_guang",
      "speaker_name": "水灵光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他没有死，他没有死……他……他永远都不会死的……。",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 453
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "speaker_name": "易清菊",
      "listener": "char_shui_ling_guang",
      "text": "妹子，你会水么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 427,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "speaker_name": "易清菊",
      "listener": "char_shui_ling_guang",
      "text": "傻孩子，你不会水，怎能救他？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "speaker_name": "易清菊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们都是死人么？为什么不下水去救人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 437
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "蜂女",
      "listener": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "text": "我们与他有什么交情，为什么要冒着生命的危险，下去救他？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 441
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qing_ju",
      "speaker_name": "易清菊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好狠毒的女人，你！你们竟忍心见死不救？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "李二姐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他若也不识水性，必然跃下去就死了，我们跃下救他，最多也不过能捞上他的尸体而已。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "李二姐",
      "listener": "char_nv_chuan_jia",
      "text": "八妹，你要做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nv_chuan_jia",
      "speaker_name": "杨八妹",
      "listener": "char_xing_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "救他。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "李二姐",
      "listener": "char_nv_chuan_jia",
      "text": "你疯了？你虽会水性，但这黄河的水，岂是长江可比，你何苦冒险下去……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_ling_guang",
      "speaker_name": "水灵光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "求苍天多多保佑他，他……是个好人，不能死的。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_ling_guang",
      "speaker_name": "水灵光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那位姑娘亦是位好人，姑娘，你无论救不救得起他来，我都永远感激你。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 473
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快将海大少放出来，否则老夫的霹雳烈火弹，便要将你们这条船毁去了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 497
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "霹雳火这老儿竟来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "对面来的可是霹雳火老前辈？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 507
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "text": "除了老夫还有谁！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "老前辈是否也要寻我妹子玩玩？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "text": "放屁，快说海大少在哪里？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "海大少？没有看见他呀！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "text": "放屁，你再不说老夫便要放弹烧船了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 519
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "老爷子，你要烧就烧吧，你把船烧了，我就带着我妹妹们到你家去吃去睡。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 523
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "老爷子，你如没事，当可上来坐坐，我们这有酒有菜，还有……你假如嫌我的妹妹不漂亮，这里还有鬼母的女徒弟……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "老爷子，你倒是上不上来呀？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "text": "你怎么不是男子？你若是男子，嘿嘿，嘿嘿……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 545
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "对不起，只恨我娘生我下来，就是一个女孩子，要返回去都来不及了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 549
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "哎呀、哎哟、哎唷地说得滔滔不绝……老爷子，我看你不要找他了，还是上来歇歇吧！你也不是他爹，何必苦苦找他？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 565
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是了，只怕他另去了别处，也未可知。这些女子和他素无冤仇，何必害他。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "老爷子这话就对了，你倒上不上来呀？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "text": "不用了，老夫还是要去找海大少，他……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那不是他么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 575,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "海兄弟，你没事么？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "有什么事？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "没事就好了，兄弟，咱们走吧！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "先等俺算算账再走。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "你要找我算账还不容易？但你也该让我知道，到底是谁将你救出来的呀！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 593
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "text": "你要见他还不容易！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "此人在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "text": "就在舱里。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，让我瞧瞧他到底是什么三头六臂的人物。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 605
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "text": "且慢。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "你难道真的已忘记了你我的往事，真要找我算今日的账么？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 611
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "今日已不知有多少人存心要毁我了，你不帮着我，也不该帮着他们呀！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 617
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花大姑",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "无论如何，你我总有多日交情，多年来……唉，你纵要算账，又何必急在今天？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 623
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_hua_da_gu",
      "text": "好！但日后若是……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 626
    }
  ],
